{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2015/02/17/pacman改下载器.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"667f520c-7203-5f67-813a-da770ee9ae35","excerpt":"pacman改下载器 pacman默认使用wget下载，没说wget不好，在家里面总是断，所以改成aria2了 移除未安装的包 使用aria2 代替 wget 修改/etc/pacman.conf","html":"<h1>pacman改下载器</h1>\n<p>pacman默认使用wget下载，没说wget不好，在家里面总是断，所以改成aria2了</p>\n<h2>移除未安装的包</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\"># pacman -Sc</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>使用aria2 代替 wget</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\"># pacman -S aria2</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>修改/etc/pacman.conf</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">XferCommand = /usr/bin/aria2c --allow-overwrite=true -c --file-allocation=none --log-level=error -m2 --max-connection-per-server=6 --max-file-not-found=5 --min-split-size=5M --no-conf --remote-time=true --log=- --summary-interval=60 -t5 -d / -o %o %u</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2015/02/17/pacman改下载器.html","date":"February 17, 2015","title":"pacman改下载器"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2015/02/17/pacman改下载器.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2015/02/17/ArchLinux升级搜狗输入法后bug的解决方案.html","title":"ArchLinux升级搜狗输入法后bug的解决方案"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2015/03/14/LearningInThreeJS(1)基本之基本.html","title":"LearningInThreeJS(1)基本之基本"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}